{"tid":30722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲唔入黎朝拜燒山？！","createTime":"2016-12-09T09:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T11:04:33.000Z","uid":9348,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b75741cd8321070e351f5b34b1b461bbe3dbf76","tid":30722,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"http://i62.tinypic.com/2jed1qq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.tinypic.com%2F2jed1qq.jpg&h=2fe248d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我們在香港的燈神，<br />\n<br />\n願人都尊燒山的名為燈；<br />\n<br />\n願燒山的國降臨；<br />\n<br />\n願燒山的旨意行在地上，<br />\n<br />\n如同行在最新燒析。<br />\n<br />\n我們日用的人網幣，<br />\n<br />\n求燒山今日賜給我們。<br />\n<br />\n又求饒恕我們的假膠，<br />\n<br />\n因為我們饒恕得罪燒山的人。<br />\n<br />\n不叫我們遇見試探，<br />\n<br />\n拯救我們脫離港共。<br />\n<br />\n因為國度、權柄、榮耀、<br />\n<br />\n全是燒山的，直到永遠。膠們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4780b62c2f4bbb5461ca023976b99ed04ec7f721","tid":30722,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:48:31.000Z","msg":"燒山好嘢！多謝燒山！"},{"pid":"f6b498a39c2bfd7a8c9d8641c791bb83b993b8f5","tid":30722,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:50:59.000Z","msg":"蕭能夠，蕭能夠，我知牠能夠，<br />\n我知燒山能帶領我燈過一切。（x2）<br />\n<br />\n牠燈了德國首相，使IS到處走，<br />\n牠使當撈侵即當選，希拉利爬住走"},{"pid":"652e09d9a731b47e4cc29666b2097e4588676edc","tid":30722,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175fbd943042c6c86ef6948b3c26d0b8d76dd3a6","tid":30722,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:53:40.000Z","msg":"燒豬教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a417825f070a0890dceb991a64b232583f7d8bec","tid":30722,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:53:57.000Z","msg":"唔係運氣！係實力！"},{"pid":"689e86d1a271c45d0528225fbaf739fd62c4eea1","tid":30722,"uid":30203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces